(158, 110, 128, 1506110116, 'Infograghic: Social Media in Business', 'infograghic-social-media-in-business', 1, 'main', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '<p>In this lesson we analyzse an inforgraphic about the impacts/advantages/disadvantages of social media in business. How has this modern day phenomenon changed the way we do business and the way corporations run. We look to the past and the future.[nbsp]</p>\n<p><img src=\"{{file::e603e5fc-9a1e-11e7-a1b2-7017236cb443}}\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"639\"></p>', '', 'mod_article_bootstrap_container', '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '1', '', ''),
(156, 108, 128, 1506107627, 'Infographic: Illiegal Immigration in California', 'infographic-illiegal-immigration-in-california', 1, 'main', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '<p>In this lesson we analyzse an inforgraphic about the financial effects of illegal immigration from Mexico and other Latin American countries on the USA.[nbsp]</p>\n<p><img src=\"files/Content/Galleries/Articles/Infographic_California/4254244700_97cc35b4ff_z.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"365\"></p>', '', 'mod_article_bootstrap_container', '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '1', '', ''),
(157, 109, 128, 1506108956, 'Infograghic: Who owns antarctica', 'infograghic-who-owns-antarctica', 1, 'main', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '<p>A look at the details on Antarctica. Does anybody live there? Is it really a country and what goes on down there? Although the continent is not permanently inhabited by anybody, it does have multiple research stations and it\'s vaste swathes of territory are hotly disputed</p>\n<p><img src=\"files/Content/Galleries/Articles/Infographic_Antarctica/12435638524_5ea9578f0f_z.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\"></p>', '', 'mod_article_bootstrap_container', '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '1', '', ''),
