(15, 1506108687, 'tl_page', 108, '1506108321', 'Franz Neumann', 'franz@gmaifdfasdfl.de', '', '<p>This is a very interesting question. The topic has changed some now. Trump is in power and is wanting to building a wall on the Mexico border and always shows himself to be a hostile to china. This is a wrong atttitude and shows the shifting tmes. China will be the next big world power and america cannot do anything about it. Americans in the south of USA are just blaming the bad times on immigrants, but it\'s not problem, as always.</p>', '1', 1, '<p>I don\'t really think Trump will build a wall and if he does it will be a shoddy shadow of his promise. Many claim that if Trump doesn\'t build it, he won\'t win the next election. This is another interesting question and if he really doesn\'t get it done, his success will depend on how well he can manipulate the voting population with fear and keep their phoney dream alive[nbsp]</p>', '1', '::1', '');
