(789, 156, 'tl_article', 896, 1506107351, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:26:\"Let us know what you think\";}', '<p>What do you think will happen in the future. Some theories suggest there will be an emormous wealth shift. Meaning that China and Asia will become the rich modern countries, the new first world; whilst Europe and America become poor third world countries whose citizens mass-migrate to China in search of work.</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
