(478, 6, 'tl_news', 1152, 1505847396, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:23:\"Adventures in Barcelona\";}', '<p>In Barcelona I stayed in a small youth hostel near the center. I enjoy my stay quite a lot, although it was a very quiet hostel and it was the winter season, so very few tourists. I mostly saw city travellers, many from Asia, they didn\'t talk to us Western people, just went out in the day in their expensive clothes and went to bed early at night. I did get to know a hot Chinese chick though. She was nice[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(479, 6, 'tl_news', 1280, 1505847553, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:31:\"Exploring the city of Barcelona\";}', '<p>I rented a bike for 5 days or so and explored the entire city. The city was so big and magnificent that It took 5 days to really explore it all. It\'s so damn beautiful, it was totally worth it. Barcelona is a very interesting part of Spain, it\'s the capital of Catalonia, a region of Spain with it\'s own distinct culture and language seeking it\'s independence. You can see nationanism everywhere, almost every apartment building has between 3 - 30 catalan flags hanging from the windows[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(480, 6, 'tl_news', 1536, 1505847728, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:17:\"The Cannabis club\";}', '<p>I met a great friend there, another digital nomad from Israel who is a software developer, he spends 4 months to a year in every country he visits and works all around the world. He was so smart, I felt humbled that we become great friends. He introduced me to one of the best Cannabis Clubs in the city. In Spain, marijuana is legal to buy in licenses assosiacions. I bought some verrrry nice weed and got very stoned for a few days. The city just got 3x more beautiful.[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
