(516, 11, 'tl_news', 1408, 1505903442, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:19:\"More Skype troubles\";}', '<p>Of course all this partying meant that I had a hard time with my Skype lessons. I smoked so much ganja that I began to forget the lessons I had that day or I would just oversleep from the night before. I knew that it couldn\'t go on like this or I would risk losing my clients that I liked. Again at the hostel, I had the problem of having terrible Wi-Fi, meaning I had to go out and search a place that had it better.[nbsp]</p>\n<p>The troubled in Spain is that most cafes don\'t have Wi-Fi and most of them don\'t want it either. Spanish streets are filled with traditional, basic Spanish cafeterias that have lots of old people in them and look very uninviting to tourists. The Spanish like it this way, they don\'t want uncivilized white tourists (\"giris\" in Spanish) infecting their cafes.[nbsp]</p>\n<p>I eventually found a nice modern cafe called Canada Coffe which was run by two Canadian guys. They had super Wi-Fi and nice tea so I decided to call this place my new internet home.[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(517, 11, 'tl_news', 1536, 1505903580, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:21:\"Off for a \"workation\"\";}', '<p>My next port of call was a strange place in the absolute middle of nowhere. A very strange place in Spain that is so un-Spanish that I[nbsp]have a hard time calling it Spain. I was leaving with my friend Toby to focus on our online businesses away from the party life of Alicante at the hostel.[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(523, 12, 'tl_news', 1024, 1505915127, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:15:\"Barking mad BnB\";}', '<p>For the first week of my stay in Almeria, I decided I would go for another AirBnB and so I booked a nice looking room with a Chilean lady in Almeria. It was alright for the first few days, I got used to the annoying dog and its barking. But with no friends in Almeria and no beach to chill at, I become bored quickly. I started to think about that beautiful girl I met on the bus and wonder why she wasn\'t calling me. To take my mind off all this I went walking around the small and beautiful city of Almeria.[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(524, 12, 'tl_news', 1152, 1505915937, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:38:\"My first apartment with Spanish people\";}', '<p>Within 3 days I had had enough of this woman and her fucking dogs. As if one loud scraggly dog wasn\'t enough to annoy her guests, the bloody woman had to go out and get more dogs. She said she used some app for dog-sitting, basically taking care of other peoples dogs whilst they aren\'t at home, and for this she got [nbsp]a bit of money.</p>\n<p>I searched around online a bit, in Spain you can\'t just send a message over a website to a landlord, you have to call them. This was a bit scary for me as it was actually my first time every speaking Spanish on the phone. It\'s always way harder on the telephone for some reason. The Spanish part was horribly embarassing, but she spoke English and told me to come for a viewing. I went, I liked the tennants, they liked me, so I moved in that very day (and paid the rent 3 days later)</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
