(597, 120, 'tl_article', 384, 1506071742, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h3\";s:5:\"value\";s:31:\"Why did this building collapse?\";}', '<p>On September the 11th, 2001, the World Trade Center in New York was attacked by two jet airplanes which crashed into Tower 1 and Tower 2. Both buildings totally collapsed within the next few hours. What many people however do not know about is the collapse of a third skyscraper on that day, this skyscraper was Tower 7. It was not hit by a plane, but still collapsed in almost exactly the same way as Tower 1 and Tower 2. It happened around 7 hours after the twin towers fell and nobody was inside the building at the time. Many are doubtful if the twin towers really collapsed because of the impact of the planes. Many physicists, engineers and architects agree it would be impossible for such a perfect collapse to happen this way. Whatever you believe, looking at the collapse of Tower 7 may change your opinion and open your eyes[nbsp]<br><br>Below is a short video of WTC 7 collapsing</p>', '', 0x24e1e54c7d9311e7b1baec9b4278947f, '', '', 'a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"100\";i:1;s:3:\"100\";i:2;s:3:\"box\";}', 'a:5:{s:6:\"bottom\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"left\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"right\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"top\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"unit\";s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'right', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
