(715, 120, 'tl_article', 608, 1506082083, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:37:\"The government tennants of Building 7\";}', '<p>C.I.A Central Intelligence Agency, Secret Service, Immigration and Naturalization Service, Securities and Exchange Commission, D.O.D Department of Defence.</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, 'bwa-GtWp4h4', NULL, 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(600, 120, 'tl_article', 640, 1506081263, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:31:\"Has this every happened before?\";}', '<p>Almost never. No such building has ever fallen down so perfectly and from such a small amount of damage. [nbsp]Below are three examples of buildings which suffered much worse fires. These fires burned for hours and the buildings still did not fall down. The inner steel structures of the buildings were too strong. Steel is a very strong material and it needs very high temperatures to melt steel. This is why demolitions are usually done with explosives. Many people claim that the Twin Towers were destroyed by a very powerful and sophisticated explosive called Nanothermite. The only way of melting steel in such a way. Nanothermite is so expensive and difficult to make that they can only be made in government laboratories.</p>\n<p>The images below show various examples of similar steel-framed buildings, the fires in these buidlings were obviously a lot worse than the fires in Building 7, and they burned a lot longer..yet these buildings stood</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, 'bwa-GtWp4h4', NULL, 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
