(716, 145, 'tl_article', 128, 1506083801, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:30:\"The rise of digital currencies\";}', '<p>Bitcoin is a digital[nbsp]<u>currency</u>[nbsp]which uses a new form of technology. It is not like British Pounds or Euros because Bitcoins do not exist as[nbsp]<u>notes</u>[nbsp]or as[nbsp]<u>coins</u>. They exists only as digital money and is stored on servers over the internet.</p>\n<p>Many people are[nbsp]<u>suspicious</u>[nbsp]of Bitcoin because they cannot see or touch it and need the internet to use it,[nbsp]<u>whereas</u>[nbsp]other people claim that Bitcoin is the currency of the future and is a good investment because it will become more valuable in the future. An interesting fact is that 95% of all the money in the world is digital or some kind of[nbsp]<u>promissory note</u>, this means that only 5% of all money can be held in your hands.</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
