(720, 145, 'tl_article', 640, 1506084118, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:9:\"Questions\";}', '<p class=\"question\">- Do you think all currencies will be digital in the future?</p>\n<p class=\"question\">- If money only exists as digital money, does it exist at all?</p>\n<p class=\"question\">- What is the advantage/disadvantage of having millions of records on the internet instead of having records controlled by the banks?</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:9:\"questions\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(731, 145, 'tl_article', 704, 1506085006, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:33:\"Which banks keep BitCoin records?\";}', '<p>No banks do. The records are kept on millions of private computers and servers. People who keep Bitcoin records are called Bitcoin Miners and the records are called \"blocks\". Anyone and everyone can be a Bitcoin Miner and miners can slowly earn Bitcoins by doing keeping these records.</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(721, 145, 'tl_article', 896, 1506084148, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:21:\"What about inflation?\";}', '<p>All currencies today[nbsp]<u>fall under the category</u>[nbsp]of Fiat Currencies. That means that these currencies are not[nbsp]<u>backed by</u>[nbsp]gold or silver or anything valuable (a.k.a commodities). What does this mean? It means that governments can print as much money as they like and cause inflation!</p>\n<p>There is only a limited number of Bitcoins in existance, and most of them have not yet been mined (like Gold). So although the value of Bitcoin goes up and down, this value cannot be directly controlled by the government by printing more or less mon</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
