(724, 146, 'tl_article', 128, 1506083439, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:28:\"From communism to capitalism\";}', '<p>We all know that China is a country with a strong economy. It is a country who’s economy has grown very rapidly since the 1950’s. Before and during the second world war the country had been a very poor country. China always had it’s problems. It was invaded by the Japanese in WW2, it suffered horrible famine and a dysfunctional economy under Chairman Mao and Communism. Only the 1970’s did China being to accept and take on capitalism. China transformed itself under this new doctrine. One big had changed. People were now allowed to open their own businesses.</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
