(726, 146, 'tl_article', 384, 1506083439, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:11:\"On the rise\";}', '<p>China, a country with an enormous wealth of natural and human resources, was able to make rapid economic gains. It had billions of people who were used to working in horrible conditions. These people could now be used in factories. Those who bought the factories and started successful businesses became rich very fast.</p>\n<p>Today China is a country with a strong economy. Many people fear that it could overtake the economy of America (United States) and become the worlds biggest economy and the worlds strongest superpower!</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
(727, 146, 'tl_article', 640, 1506083439, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:9:\"China 2.0\";}', '<p>China knows that technology is the future. It knows that it will become the strongest industry in the world. It knows that when the oil runs out, America and the West will be up shit creak without a paddle. China invests heavily technology. Have you spoken to an Indian call center or seen stories of cheap Indian programmers working like factory workers, churning out program after program. China knows that India could be the next global superpower with which it will compete for world domination. India has a population of 1.1 Billion, while China has 1.3 Billion. India has many natural resources and lots of cheap labour. But India has many problems and that is why it’s not as powerful as China...yet.</p>\n<p>Workers of China’s technoogy industry are not like workers of Americas tech industry, Silicone Valley. In Silicone Valley, most workers are nowadays imported. Many come from Europe, China of course, India and Japan. In China however, most of the tech-talent is homegrown.</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
