(746, 145, 'tl_article', 960, 1506085613, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:16:\"Some market data\";}', '<p>Have a look at the Bitcoin price graph. Is the price going up or down at the moment?[nbsp]</p>\n<p>Over the last 2 years, the price of BitCoin has fluctuated enormously. When bringing up the topic of BitCoin with many people, they often remark about how somebody offered them to buy 1 Bitcoin at 300 dollars and how they could have been rich if they would have taken it.[nbsp]</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', ''),
