(773, 154, 'tl_article', 896, 1506106071, 'text', 'a:2:{s:4:\"unit\";s:2:\"h1\";s:5:\"value\";s:0:\"\";}', '<p>We are a hotel located in Penzance, Cornwall. We are welcome all guests from all country in the world. Here at our hotel we has much things to do for childs and for adults. In Penzance there are lots of restaurants and shops. The beach is also in the near and you can drive by train to other towns like St.Ives or Truro.[nbsp]<br><br>At our hotel, you can make much fun and enjoy free eat in the morning. For breakfast, we have also a food card for children and also a card for older peoples who enjoy different eat.</p>', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'above', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:11:\"text-letter\";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', '', '', '', 'ascending', 0, '', '', '', '', 'com_default', 0, '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '');
