(40, 71, 1506266639, 'Killing the parasite Facebook', 'http://localhost/ContaoMeta.0.1/index.php/news-archive-general/killing-the-parasite-facebook.html', 'Killing the parasite Facebook I recently have deleted my Facebook and Whatsapp accounts. For many years I had trouble with this. I tried to delete my Facebook account many times with no success Home Killing the parasite of Facebook As mentioned, I recently removed myself from Facebook and Whatsapp. These are probably two of the best things that I\'ve done in a long time. I\'ve always known the evil sides of these services. After years of observing how they affected my life and reading enough about Facebooks data mining and social experimentation, I decided it was time to stop feed this filthy parasite my precious personal data Growing up with Facebook Facebook is something I can really say I\'ve grown up with, not like the children of this generation, but almost. I began using Facebook when it became popular in my school at around age 14. A very vulnerable age. I was completely hooked to the flurry of information and attention I was getting and could give. I could look at all my crushes, they could look at me, I could stalk people, I could remember peoples names and birthdays. How fantastic...it seemed I never stopped to think that Facebook was genuinely spying on me. I never read the terms and conditons. I didn\'t give a shit. Now Facebook knows almost everything about me such as Who my friends are Who my parents are Where I lived How I look My entire personality Living without it Many people have trouble deleting Facebook, we always want to, but don\'t want to feel left out. If this is the case then you should take a closer look at your life. Why do you have friends that make you use an evil service? A service which sells your personal information to advertisers and is probably the biggest driver in the direction of transforming society into a Orwellian techno-police state, with the cameras everywhere recognising your face through Facebook, police predicting who will be a criminal based on their Facebook and god knows what else diabolical things artificial intelligence and Facebook can achieve together Contao Demo,', 15.34, 'f4b793cbe927ceb85d301b489e48f8b7', '', 0x30, 'en'),
(41, 71, 1506266640, '09/11 Terror Attack', 'http://localhost/ContaoMeta.0.1/index.php/news-archive-general/id-09-11-terror-attack.html', '09/11 Terror Attack Today it\'s been sixteen years ago that the Twin Towers in Manhattan, New York, were hit by an airplane. Home The Terror Attack of 09/11 Sixteen years ago on this day, the 11th September, an airplane crashed into the famous Twin Towers in New York. 3000 people died, and the world was left with a shock that for many resulted in a trauma. Even if you haven\'t been directly and personally affected, may it be possible that behind this date, there is a story bigger than its already devastating effects on its own? Could it be that there are actual psychological effects on not only a small number of naturally traumatized relatives and friends, but also on a whole continent - or the world which has watched the news? In a soon upcoming article, we will address this question and take the facts into further inquiry. Contao Demo,', 14.24, '49b494b633ab4c83c8af2f8593cb1bdb', '', 0x30, 'en'),
(42, 71, 1506266641, 'Next Stay: Alicante', 'http://localhost/ContaoMeta.0.1/index.php/news-archive-general/next-stay-alicante.html', 'Next Stay: Alicante Alicante is always worth a visit and not to be explored in only a couple of days. Have a look where the journey goes to! Home Next Stay: Alicante Alicante is always worth a visit and not to be explored in only a couple of days. To really get a feeling for this city you have to stay longer - this one will be about three weeks. But how do you explore a city best - by sleeping under the stars on a mountain, renting a youth hostel or Airbnb, or even checking into a hotel? This time, we opted for a very reasonably priced Airbnb. Our host who shares her apartment with us is an artist and the whole apartment is furnished with beautiful portrait paintings. Staying in an Airbnb isn\'t only a fantastic opportunity for getting to know such interesting people, but also improve your Spanish language skills, because Airbnb\'s are often rented by them. Contao Demo', 13.72, 'd202764d3e7182e277337b829b50974e', '', 0x30, 'en'),
